data.description: Come take a look at this beautiful 3 bedroom & 2 bath home located in the wonderful gated community of Springlake Village. This property sits on 0.39 of an acre and has no neighboring properties in the back. The home’s interior is very spacious and also includes a bonus Florida room. The exterior of the home has a screened in porch and a wooden deck. The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet, and the master bath has a separate shower and bathtub. There is a laundry room located inside, and the garage is a two-car garage. The home was re-roofed with brand new shingles in 2018, a brand new HVAC system installed in December 2021, a new sprinkler system, and a new hot water heater. Springlake Village is a gated community and includes many desirable amenities for its residents’ use, including two swimming pools,  playgrounds, a gym, a video game arcade, dog park, tennis, shuffleboard and even more. The home is conveniently located too, close to Orlando International Airport and just a few minutes drive away from medical city. Act fast and schedule your showing today!
